bilingual.source: Now it so happened that a great, green water dragon was passing by.
bilingual.target: 现在恰好有一条巨大的绿色水龙经过。

bilingual.source: The train passing by made the ground zhen.
bilingual.target: 火车经过时使地面震动。

bilingual.source: He would often leer at the women passing by.
bilingual.target: 他经常色迷迷地看经过的女人。

bilingual.source: The yob threw a bottle at the passing car.
bilingual.target: 那个流氓向经过的汽车扔了一瓶子。

bilingual.source: There are often dump trucks passing by on this road.
bilingual.target: 这条路上经常有翻斗车经过。

bilingual.source: The sensor can cnt the number of cars passing by.
bilingual.target: 传感器可以计数经过的汽车数量。

bilingual.source: The rumble of the train passing by shook the house.
bilingual.target: 火车经过时的隆隆声震动了房子。

bilingual.source: The vibrations from the passing train shook the house.
bilingual.target: 经过的火车的振动使房子摇晃。

bilingual.source: The stranded sailors were rescued by a passing ship.
bilingual.target: 被困的水手被一艘经过的船救了。

bilingual.source: He stood on the shore and wave at the passing boats.
bilingual.target: 他站在岸边向经过的船只挥手。

list.abstract: 冰球运动技术术语。传接球是完成进攻战术配合的主要手段，也是个人技术与全队战术配合之间的纽带，包括传球和接球。

yingyinNormal.en: Do you remember a freight train passing by just before the explosion？Yes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你记不记得爆炸时正好有辆货运列车经过？记得。

yingyinNormal.en: So sorry that I'm late, but I made the mistake of passing through the Wyeth exhibit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 抱歉我迟到了，我在经过惠氏的展览时迷路了。

yingyinNormal.en: And lucky for you, your new favorite hero, old Baloo, here, just happened to be passing by.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你可真走运，你真心崇拜的英雄老巴鲁碰巧经过那儿。

yingyinNormal.en: We were passing by on our way home. We thought we'd say hi. In the middle of the night?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们在回家的路上经过这里，想着过来打声招呼。大半夜的？

yingyinNormal.en: So, the plan is for me to use that to go into orbit just as the Hermes is passing, and I guess they catch me in space.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以现在的计划就是我用它飞到火星轨道，正好当赫尔墨斯好经过， 然后在宇宙中接住我。

yingyinNormal.en: The explosion was timed to engulf the passing freight train, which means, the bomber had to be watching both trains when the call was made. 52 callers, one of those is our bomber.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在爆炸发生的时刻货车刚好经过，这表明设弹人是在可见两车的情况下打的电话。52个人，其中一个是设弹人。

yingyinNormal.en: So am I. His passing makes me feel bad.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我也是，他的离世让我，好伤心呢。

yingyinNormal.en: I was just passing through. I don't want any trouble.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我只是路过而已，不想惹什么麻烦。

yingyinNormal.en: It gives the petal an iridescence, to attract passing insects.
yingyinNormal.zh: 使花瓣显得色彩斑斓，引得往来昆虫为之驻足。

yingyinNormal.en: But you must try, Master. With every passing day we become less human.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但你必须尝试，掌握。日子一天天过去我们越来越不像人。

yingyinNormal.en: If I were you, I'd be more concerned about what they are passing off as chicken.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果我是你，我会更关心他们是拿什么假冒了鸡丁。

yingyinNormal.en: We have only three passing scores on the deep space navigation test. Alai, Bean and Ender.
yingyinNormal.zh: 只有三个学员通过了深空导航测试，有阿莱和小豆子，还有安德。

yingyinNormal.en: A series of anonymous wire transfers originating in Dubai and passing through a front company in the Comoros.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有人通过科摩罗的一个皮包公司匿名从迪拜给他们电汇资金。

yingyinNormal.en: No, but your ability to perceive their existence is conditional on you passing the second and third barriers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，但对你来说卧室的存在是有条件的，你要通过第二和第三关。

yingyinNormal.en: George has got a medal. Pass the parcel. Oh dear, George isn't passing the parcel. No, George. That's Zaza's medal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治也得到了一块奖牌。快把包裹传出去。哦，糟糕，乔治不想把包裹传给别人。不行乔治，这块奖牌是莎莎的才对。

yingyinNormal.en: I believe the Sichuan palace has been passing off orange chicken as tangerine chicken and I intend to confront them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我认为四川菜馆故意用香橙鸡丁来假冒陈皮鸡丁，所以我要去对峙。

yingyinNormal.en: They arise chiefly from what is passing at the time, and though I do sometimes amuse myself with arranging such little elegant compliments.
yingyinNormal.zh: 大半是看临时的情形想起来的，不过有时候我也自己跟自己打趣，预先想好一些很好的小恭维话，平常有机会就拿来应用。

yingyinNormal.en: Since it was just me and Mama and we had all these empty rooms, Mama decided to let those rooms out, mostly to people passing through, like from, Mobile, Montgomery, places like that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 房子只有我和妈妈住，我们有好多空房间，妈妈将这些空房出租给路过的人住，比如从莫比镇、或蒙哥马利镇来的人。

yingyinNormal.en: You know, I mean the first time he said it we were just passing each other in the hallway, so I didn't say anything. And then the next time he said, "Hey Toby, do you want a doughnut?" And I wanted a doughnut.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第一次我们错身而过，所以我什么都没说，第二次他说“托比，你要吃甜甜圈吗？”我想吃甜甜圈。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全四级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: The morning sun rose and with every <highlight>passing</highlight> minute, he lost more strength.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 太阳在早上升起来了，每过一分钟，它的强度就更弱。

examination_example.sentence: To a certain degree, we can understand and control our experience of time <highlight>passing</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在一定程度上，我们可以理解和掌控我们对时间流逝的感受。

examination_example.sentence: In the A, B, C, D and F grading system,the first four letters are typically considered <highlight>passing</highlight> grades.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在A、B、C、D和F评分系统中，前四个字母通常被认为是及格分数。

examination_example.sentence: When you first started to learn Chinese, I thought it was nothing but a <highlight>passing</highlight> fad (一时的狂热).
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当你刚开始学中文的时候，我以为这只是一时的狂热。
